<plot>Each year the EU donates approx. 46 billion Euro to agriculture in EU-countries. Almost half the money available to the EU. Many farmers, especially the small ones, have become dependent of the support. But now the donations are being reduced. Heavily. The future for many farmers does not look bright.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?203196</url></doc>
